@page "/contact"
<section>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-6">
                <img
                    src="assets/img/network.png" alt="testimonial-img"
                    class="w-100">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-6">
                <div class="testimonial ">
                    <h5 class="testimonial__subtitle mb-4">Contact Us</h5>
                    <h2 class="testimonial__title mb-4">
                        Food <span>Delivery</span>
                    </h2>
                    <p class="review__text">
                        Thank you for considering our food delivery service. We value your feedback, questions, and concerns. Please feel free to reach out to us using any of the following methods:

                        Phone:
                        Call our customer service hotline at [Phone Number]. Our dedicated representatives are available [Hours of Operation] to assist you with any inquiries regarding our food delivery service. Whether you need help placing an order, tracking a delivery, or have any other questions, we are here to help.

                        Email:
                        Send us an email at [Email Address]. Feel free to write to us about your food delivery experience, menu suggestions, or any other inquiries you may have. Our team will respond to your email as soon as possible, typically within [Response Timeframe].

                        Online Contact Form:
                        Visit our website [Website URL] and navigate to the "Contact Us" page. Fill out the contact form with your name, email address, subject, and message. Provide us with as much detail as possible so that we can better assist you. Our team will review your submission and respond accordingly.

                        Social Media:
                        You can also reach out to us on our social media channels. Follow us on [Social Media Platform] at [Social Media Handle] and send us a direct message. We are active on social media and will do our best to respond promptly to your inquiries or feedback.

                        Live Chat:
                        Visit our website [Website URL] and look for the live chat option. Our customer service representatives are available to chat with you in real-time and provide immediate assistance. Simply click on the chat icon and start a conversation.

                        We appreciate your interest in our food delivery service and are committed to ensuring a pleasant experience for our customers. Your satisfaction is our top priority, and we look forward to addressing any questions or concerns you may have.

                        Thank you for choosing us for your food delivery needs. We value your support and strive to continuously improve our service.

                        Sincerely,

                        [Your Company Name]
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>